title: Another great feat at the just concluded National conference tagged ITAC'22 01
content: The National TIMSAN body in conjunction with International Organization of Tijanniyah Brotherhood (IOTB) recorded yet another great feat at the just concluded National conference tagged ITAC'22. The National Conference is an annual convergence of all members of TIMSAN across all local zawiyahs, states and geopolitical zones in the country and this 12th edition is yet another avenue where all participants explored the ideas of the future wholly and healthily through various enriching programs like several entrepreneurship programs, business summits and tech training sessions on Cybersecurity.
